---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ConsultationCTA from '@/components/ConsultationCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Proline128 — The Ergonomic Grid Kitchen"
  description="Pronorm Proline128: the innovative 128mm grid planning system that makes any desired height a reality. Combine with handles, push-to-open, or mix with Y‑line and X‑line for maximum individuality."
>
  <section class="collection-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/images/product-lines/proline-classic-handles.webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(26,26,26,0.8) 0%, rgba(26,26,26,0.2) 70%); z-index: 2;"></div>
    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 3;" class="container">
      <span class="overline animate-in" style="color: var(--color-copper);">Product Line</span>
      <h1 class="animate-in animate-in-delay-1" style="color: var(--color-white);">Proline128</h1>
      <p class="animate-in animate-in-delay-2" style="color: var(--color-sand); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; max-width: 50ch; margin-top: 0.75rem;">The ergonomic grid kitchen. An innovative 128mm planning system where any desired height becomes a reality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Design Philosophy -->
  <section class="section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="overline">Design Philosophy</span>
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Precision Meets<br/>Personality</h2>
          <hr class="divider" style="margin: 1.5rem 0;" />
          <p>The innovative Proline128 grid planning system has convincing answers to all your furnishing questions and wishes. Using the 128mm grid steps and in combination with various plinth heights, any desired height becomes a reality.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Perfectly thought out and personalised to you, your kitchen becomes a place where cooking and living become a wonderful experience. With this product line, functionality and aesthetics merge into a harmonious unit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <div style="aspect-ratio:3/4;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/product-lines/front-joint-pattern.jpg" alt="Proline128 Grid Detail" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Combinability -->
  <section class="section bg-ivory">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="detail-grid reverse">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div style="aspect-ratio:4/3;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/product-lines/handleless-cross-product.webp" alt="Proline128 Combined with Y-line" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="overline">Maximum Individuality</span>
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Combine Freely</h2>
          <hr class="divider" style="margin: 1.5rem 0;" />
          <p>The grid allows Pronorm product lines to be combined effortlessly, enabling maximum individuality. Cabinets with handles in Proline128 can be easily combined with handleless cabinets — X‑line, Y‑line, or even Proline128 with push-to-open.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">This means a single kitchen can feature handled base cabinets with a handleless tall unit run, or a handleless island paired with handled wall cabinets. The 128mm grid ensures everything aligns perfectly regardless of combination.</p>
          <div class="combo-tags" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <span class="combo-tag">Proline128 + Y‑line</span>
            <span class="combo-tag">Proline128 + X‑line</span>
            <span class="combo-tag">Proline128 + Push-to-Open</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Handle Collection -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="overline">Handle Collection 2026</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Curated Hardware</h2>
      <p class="subtitle" style="margin: 1rem auto 2rem; max-width: 55ch;">Pronorm's dedicated Handle Collection offers a curated range of premium handles designed to complement every front colour and material in the Proline128 range.</p>
      <div class="handle-grid">
        <div class="handle-card reveal">
          <img src="/images/projects/modern-black/gold-handle.webp" alt="Pronorm Bar Handle" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;" />
          <h4 style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Bar Handles</h4>
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-warm-gray);">Linear, architectural profiles</p>
        </div>
        <div class="handle-card reveal">
          <img src="/images/projects/country-kitchen/drawer-fronts.webp" alt="Pronorm Knobs" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;" />
          <h4 style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Knobs</h4>
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-warm-gray);">Classic, compact elegance</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proline128 Plus -->
  <section class="section bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="overline">Enhanced Ergonomics</span>
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Proline128 Plus</h2>
          <hr class="divider" style="margin: 1.5rem 0;" />
          <p>Proline128 plus enables maximum and customised ergonomics above and beyond the standard — whether for larger personalities or for even more design impact with a low plinth.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Proline128 allows you to combine ergonomics and versatility in ways no other kitchen system can match. Every height, every proportion, every combination is yours to define.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <div style="aspect-ratio:4/3;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/product-lines/extra-wide-drawers.jpg" alt="Proline128 Plus Ergonomics" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Video -->
  <section class="section bg-ivory">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="overline">See It In Motion</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Proline128 Construction</h2>
      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl); aspect-ratio: 16/9; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--color-black);">
        <iframe width="100%" height="100%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vzDFdD4WtkM" title="Pronorm Kitchen Construction" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen style="border:0;"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Downloads -->
  <section class="section bg-ivory text-center">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <span class="overline">Resources</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Proline128 Downloads</h2>
      <p class="subtitle" style="margin: 1rem auto 2rem; max-width: 50ch;">Explore our product specifications, handle collection, and full brochure for the Proline128 collection.</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/downloads/Product-Range-Pro-Classic-2026-EN.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline" style="gap: 0.5rem;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          Pro &amp; Classic Product Range (PDF)
        </a>
        <a href="/downloads/Handle-Collection-2026-EN.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline" style="gap: 0.5rem;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          Handle Collection 2026 (PDF)
        </a>
        <a href="/downloads/Create-Your-World-Brochure-2026-EN.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline" style="gap: 0.5rem;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          2026 Brochure (PDF)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="overline">Gallery</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Proline128 Kitchens</h2>
      <div class="project-grid" style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl);">
        <div style="aspect-ratio:16/10;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/gallery/new-generation-family.jpg" alt="Proline128 Modern with Handles" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        <div style="aspect-ratio:1;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/product-lines/front-extension.jpg" alt="Proline128 Handle Detail" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        <div style="aspect-ratio:1;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/gallery/open-plan-family-l-island.jpg" alt="Proline128 Combined Design" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        <div style="aspect-ratio:1;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;"><img src="/images/style-gallery/pronorm-kitchen-country-house-frame-front-mediterranean-grey-Beitragsbild.jpg" alt="Country House Frame" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
        <div style="aspect-ratio:16/10;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;grid-column:span 2;"><img src="/images/style-gallery/pronorm-bright-kitchen-japandi-style-wood-storage-room-BEITRAGSBILD.jpg" alt="Japandi Oak Kitchen" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ConsultationCTA heading="Experience Proline128 In Person" text="Visit an authorized dealer to explore the 128mm grid system and see the full Handle Collection 2026." />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .collection-hero { position: relative; min-height: 65vh; display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .detail-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-4xl); align-items: center; }
  .detail-grid.reverse > :first-child { order: 1; }
  .detail-grid.reverse > :last-child { order: 2; }
  .handle-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-xl); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .combo-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .combo-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-sand);
    color: var(--color-graphite);
  }
  .project-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--space-md); }
  .project-grid .img-placeholder { transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); cursor: pointer; }
  .project-grid .img-placeholder:hover { transform: scale(1.03); }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .handle-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); max-width: 100%; } }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .detail-grid, .project-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .detail-grid.reverse > :first-child { order: 2; }
    .detail-grid.reverse > :last-child { order: 1; }
    .handle-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
